@CLF.Server_HostAddress = http://localhost:5113

GET {{CLF.Server_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json

###

### Fire Events API Tests

### 1. Get townships with active fire events today
GET https://localhost:7001/api/fire-events/townships/active-today
Accept: application/json

### 2. Get fire events for a single township
GET https://localhost:7001/api/fire-events/township/Springfield
Accept: application/json

### 3. Get fire events for a single township with filters
GET https://localhost:7001/api/fire-events/township/Springfield?fromDate=2024-01-01&status=active&minIntensity=5
Accept: application/json

### 4. Get fire events for multiple townships
GET https://localhost:7001/api/fire-events/townships?townships=Springfield,Riverside,Oakland
Accept: application/json

### 5. Get fire events by bounding box
GET https://localhost:7001/api/fire-events/bbox?minLon=-120&minLat=25&maxLon=-60&maxLat=55
Accept: application/json

### 6. Get fire events by bounding box with filters
GET https://localhost:7001/api/fire-events/bbox?minLon=-120&minLat=25&maxLon=-60&maxLat=55&status=active&minIntensity=3
Accept: application/json

### 7. Get township summary
GET https://localhost:7001/api/fire-events/township/Springfield/summary
Accept: application/json

### 8. Health check
GET https://localhost:7001/api/fire-events/health
Accept: application/json

